/* Windows resource script: embeds the app icon into iknowwhatisaw.exe so it
 * shows in the taskbar, Explorer, and the Steam library.  The lowest-numbered
 * ICON resource is the one Windows uses as the application icon.  Regenerate
 * the .ico with:  python3 tools/make_icon.py
 */
1 ICON "iknowwhatisaw.ico"
